official_title: A bill to declare a portion of the Wakulla River, Fla., as a nonnavigable water of the United States.

summary.text: Declares that a portion of the headwaters of the Wakulla River in Florida which is utilized as a breeding ground by order of the Florida Game and Fresh Water Fish Commission is to be a non-navigable water of the United States.

titles.title: A bill to declare a portion of the Wakulla River, Fla., as a nonnavigable water of the United States.
